long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
New Page tab inspired by safari start page on MacOS. Still in early development, feedback much appreciated.

Features:
 + View and navigate your bookmarks.
 + Auto icons for your bookmarks.
 + Edit, rename, and remove your bookmarks.
 + View your Frequently visited pages.
 + Set Background Images.
